OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FThe Government has announced a public
OL,7,Finquiry into a violent confrontation
OL,8,Fbetween striking miners and police
OL,9,Fwhich became known as the Battle of
OL,10,FOrgreave.
OL,12,FCampaigners have long fought for an
OL,13,Finvestigation into the police's
OL,14,Factions during and after clashes at
OL,15,Fthe South Yorkshire coking plant on 18
OL,16,FJune 1984.
