OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FDozens of people were injured and 95
OL,7,Fpicketers were arrested and charged
OL,8,Fwith riot and violent disorder, but
OL,9,Fall charges were later dropped after
OL,10,Fevidence was discredited.
OL,12,FThe inquiry, expected to launch in the
OL,13,Fautumn, will investigate the events
OL,14,Fsurrounding the incident and will have
OL,15,Fpowers to compel people to provide
OL,16,Finformation where necessary, the Home
OL,17,FOffice said.
