OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FThe Rt Revd Dr Pete Wilcox, the Bishop
OL,7,Fof Sheffield, has agreed to chair the
OL,8,Finquiry, which the Home Office said is
OL,9,Fintended to "aid the public's
OL,10,Funderstanding of how the events on the
OL,11,Fday, and immediately after, came to
OL,12,Fpass".
OL,14,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said what
OL,15,Fhappened at Orgreave "cast a shadow
OL,16,Fover communities in Yorkshire and
OL,17,Fother mining areas".
OL,26,@qD@MOUtD@EO]wD@VOUyD@SO]
