OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FMs Cooper added: "The violent scenes
OL,7,Fand subsequent prosecutions raised
OL,8,Fconcerns that have been left
OL,9,Funanswered for decades, and we must
OL,10,Fnow establish what happened.
OL,12,F"I pay tribute to the campaigners who
OL,13,Fnever stopped in their search for
OL,14,Ftruth and justice, and I look forward
OL,15,Fto continuing to work with them as we
OL,16,Fbuild an inquiry that gets the answers
OL,17,Fthey and their communities deserve."
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOUyD@dO]
