OL,6,FThe Home Office said formal
OL,7,Fconsultation between the Home
OL,8,FSecretary and the Rt Revd Wilcox on
OL,9,Fthe inquiry's terms of reference has
OL,10,Fbegun.
OL,12,FThe Rt Revd Wilcox said he did not
OL,13,F"underestimate the weight of
OL,14,Fexpectation or the significance of the
OL,15,Ftask".
