OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FHe added: "I look forward to engaging
OL,7,Fwith stakeholders in the coming weeks
OL,8,Fover the draft terms of reference, and
OL,9,Fto working with the government to
OL,10,Fidentify experts to support me on the
OL,11,Findependent panel.
OL,13,F"I expect the panel to begin its work
OL,14,Fin the autumn, and we will endeavour
OL,15,Fto deliver an inquiry which is
OL,16,Fthorough and fair, and which will
OL,17,Funcover what happened at Orgreave as
OL,18,Fswiftly as possible."
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOUzD@UO]
