OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FThe Orgreave Truth & Justice Campaign
OL,7,F(OTJC) said it wanted to know who was
OL,8,Fresponsible for "organising and
OL,9,Fordering the deployment of multiple
OL,10,Fpolice forces, including mounted
OL,11,Fpolice armed with truncheons, shields
OL,12,Fand dogs, against striking miners".
OL,14,FThe campaign group said it wanted the
OL,15,Finquiry to find out how it was decided
OL,16,Fthat "striking miners should be
OL,17,Fattacked and arrested at Orgreave and
OL,18,Fcharged with riot and unlawful
OL,19,Fassembly, which carried heavy prison
OL,20,Fsentences".
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@bO]xD@FOU|D@JO]
