OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FIt added that it wanted to know why
OL,7,F"the police operational order for
OL,8,Fpolice deployments that day
OL,9,Fdisappeared and other evidence been
OL,10,Fdestroyed or embargoed until 2066 and
OL,11,F2071".
OL,13,FOTJC secretary, Kate Flannery, said
OL,14,Fthe announcement of an inquiry was
OL,15,F"really positive news".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@EO]wD@AOUwD@VO]
