OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FMr Kitchen added: "The events at
OL,7,FOrgreave, and throughout the strike,
OL,8,Fdestroyed the trust between the police
OL,9,Fand mining communities even now, 41
OL,10,Fyears later.
OL,12,F"It is vital that this trust is won
OL,13,Fback and the NUM believe this inquiry
OL,14,Fwill go some way to rebuilding that
OL,15,Ftrust."
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUwD@GO]
