OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FKevin Horne, a miner arrested at
OL,7,FOrgreave, said: "It is now over 41
OL,8,Fyears since a paramilitary style
OL,9,Fpolice operation was planned at
OL,10,FOrgreave and it is important to
OL,11,Fremember that some of the miners
OL,12,Fattacked and arrested there are now
OL,13,Fdead and many others are old and ill.
OL,15,F"We need a quick and thorough inquiry
OL,16,Fwith a tight timescale so that
OL,17,Fsurviving miners can at last obtain
OL,18,Fthe truth and justice they have been
OL,19,Fwaiting for."
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@AOU{D@MO]
