OL,3,CGovernment announces inquiry into
OL,4,CBattle of Orgreave
OL,6,FMayor of South Yorkshire, Oliver
OL,7,FCoppard, said the inquiry was a
OL,8,F"landmark moment for justice and
OL,9,Faccountability".
OL,11,FMr Coppard added: "The Inquiry
OL,12,Frepresents an opportunity to examine
OL,13,Fnot only the actions of South
OL,14,FYorkshire Police and other forces on
OL,15,Fthat day, but also the broader role of
OL,16,Fgovernment at the time.
OL,18,F"It's a step towards setting the
OL,19,Fhistorical record straight, ensuring
OL,20,Flessons are learned, and restoring
OL,21,Fpublic trust."
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@OO]sD@SOUzD@AOU}D@NO]
